(17, 1, NULL, 0, 'Hundred Power Trading LLC', 14, 'INV-', 2, 'INV-2025/000014', '2025-07-15 14:15:37', '2025-07-15', '2025-07-18', 3, 1700.00, 0.00, 1500.00, -200.00, 1, 'e64ff9b3ad10da1e600413514ca5b8f0', 2, '', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 'a:3:{i:0;s:1:\"1\";i:1;s:13:\"Ideal_gateway\";i:2;s:6:\"stripe\";}', NULL, 0.00, 0.00, '', 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, 'Project Completion:<br />\r\nThe branding design services, including logo, letterhead, and related brand assets, have been fully completed, revised, and approved by the client.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFile Delivery:<br />\r\nAll final files (in formats such as .AI, .PDF, .PNG, etc.) have been delivered or are ready for delivery upon final payment confirmation.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOwnership Rights:<br />\r\nFull rights and ownership of the final designs will be transferred to the client upon receipt of full payment. Until payment is cleared, all creative assets remain the property of Ziron Media FZ LLC.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNo Further Revisions:<br />\r\nAny additional edits or changes after this stage will be treated as a new task and quoted separately.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPayment Terms:<br />\r\nFull payment is due immediately upon receipt of this invoice. A late fee of AED 100 will apply for payments delayed beyond 7 days.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNon-Refundable:<br />\r\nAs the design work has been fully completed and approved, this project is non-refundable.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nShowcasing Work:<br />\r\nZiron Media reserves the right to showcase the final designs in its portfolio, social media, or website unless the client explicitly requests otherwise in writing.', 1, 'Dubai', '', '', '', 234, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, NULL),
