(3, 2, 'Urgent ', 'The tracking page for the Maxline website is being developed by their software team. We need to share the UI/UX styling details with them. Please send me the following info ASAP:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Background color<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Main heading – font, size, and color<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Subheading – font, size, and color<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Tracking input field – background color, border color, font & text color<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Track button – background color, hover color, text color, border radius<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Progress line/steps – colors for active and inactive states<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Table (tracking info) – header background & text color, row background colors, border color, font<br />\r\n<br />\r\n✅ Default font family and body text color used across the site<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease keep the design consistent with the rest of the site (font, colors, spacing). Once I get these details, I’ll forward them to Maxline’s development team.', 1, '2025-06-09 09:31:05', NULL, 1, 0);
